if you hadn't forgiven me?

29:31.904 --> 29:34.071
If I had never known

29:34.073 --> 29:37.775
What it was like
to have this?

29:37.777 --> 29:40.911
This moment,
this gift

29:40.913 --> 29:43.814
Of being so close
to you.

29:43.816 --> 29:47.584
[sniffles]
[sighs]

29:47.586 --> 29:50.187
I'm so sorry
I ever wrote it.

29:50.189 --> 29:54.958
- It came from a good place.
- No.

29:54.960 --> 29:57.327
It was cruel.

29:57.329 --> 30:00.597
[sighs]

30:05.270 --> 30:07.104
- Did I become
this person?

30:07.106 --> 30:09.673
- Oh, babe.

30:09.675 --> 30:12.876
- I dropped my friends,

30:12.878 --> 30:14.745
Second-guessed
my instincts.

30:14.747 --> 30:17.748
And worst of all,

30:17.750 --> 30:20.851
I was cruel.

30:20.853 --> 30:24.087
So, so cruel.

30:24.089 --> 30:27.391
- And young.

30:27.393 --> 30:29.593
You are not this person.

30:29.595 --> 30:32.729
