your mistakes,

30:32.731 --> 30:35.199
You took ownership
of them,

30:35.201 --> 30:36.433
You made amends.

30:36.435 --> 30:41.071
Honey, without
the bad days,

30:41.073 --> 30:43.240
We can never appreciate
the good ones.

30:43.242 --> 30:47.377
