coming your way.

30:47.379 --> 30:50.414
- [sighs]

30:50.416 --> 30:54.084
- Just do me a favor.

30:54.086 --> 30:55.185
- What?

30:55.187 --> 30:58.889
- Forgive yourself

30:58.891 --> 31:01.692
Like you forgave me.

31:01.694 --> 31:04.828
[soft music]

31:04.830 --> 31:13.136
♪

31:15.907 --> 31:19.476
- Stop being a [bleep].

31:19.478 --> 31:22.112
♪

31:22.114 --> 31:26.316
- And that's why fred can never
go to ventura county again.

31:26.318 --> 31:26.817
- [sighs]

31:26.819 --> 31:29.086
Ming, I dropped my napkin.
Can you help me?

31:29.088 --> 31:32.256
- And he can't even pick up
a napkin.

31:32.258 --> 31:34.191
- I can.

31:34.193 --> 31:37.561
But it seems like
you're stepping on it.

31:37.563 --> 31:40.097
Help me.

31:40.099 --> 31:41.665
- [groans]

31:41.667 --> 31:42.566
- What the hell
are you doing?

31:42.568 --> 31:45.102
- I'm just trying to help
my parents get to know you.

31:45.104 --> 31:46.036
- And hate me.

31:46.038 --> 31:47.037
What are you gonna
tell them next?

31:47.039 --> 31:49.940
