- Are you?

31:49.942 --> 31:53.510
- Ming ming.

31:53.512 --> 31:54.912
- [clears throat]

31:54.914 --> 31:58.348
- Shouldn't you be leaving?

31:58.350 --> 31:59.416
- Yes.

31:59.418 --> 32:03.587
