do you want me home?

32:04.889 --> 32:06.924
- Whenever.
No curfew.

32:06.926 --> 32:09.293
- What?
Why?

32:09.295 --> 32:13.530
- It's prom.

32:14.632 --> 32:17.534
- Mr. Hart,
attached is my paper.

32:17.536 --> 32:20.037
