Tense face.

33:01.780 --> 33:04.281
- I don't have tense face.
- Objectively, you do.

33:04.283 --> 33:07.250
- Objectively, you don't
know everything.

33:07.252 --> 33:08.385
- That would be
a correct statement.

33:08.387 --> 33:10.554
But in this case,
I know nerves,

33:10.556 --> 33:13.256
And I know you.

33:13.258 --> 33:17.894
- Well, if you know me,
then why am I nervous?

33:17.896 --> 33:21.565
- May I touch you?

33:21.567 --> 33:25.235
- Okay.

33:27.638 --> 33:30.107
- The rhythms of your heart
are fast and furious,

33:30.109 --> 33:31.675
Proving my first assumption
was correct.

33:31.677 --> 33:32.809
- And what assumption
was that?

33:32.811 --> 33:33.677
- The assumption
that you love me

33:33.679 --> 33:34.678
And you're afraid
to say it.

33:34.680 --> 33:36.546
- Not true.
- That wasn't a question.

33:36.548 --> 33:38.348
It was a statement.
- So what?

33:38.350 --> 33:39.783
Are you gonna
leave now?

33:39.785 --> 33:40.517
- No.
- Why not?

33:40.519 --> 33:45.022
